923	  \uses{def:Scheme_IsCechAcyclicCover, def:Scheme_HasCechToHModuleIso}
924	  For every affine open $U$, there exists an indexed cover $\mathfrak U$ with $\bigsqcup \mathfrak U_i = U$ that is Čech-acyclic and carries a comparison isomorphism.
